Drivo Privacy Policy (English)
Last updated: October 20, 2025

Drivo we operates as a platform that connects users who want to buy or sell new and used cars in Syria. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use the Drivo app or website.

1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following information:

Personal information: Name, phone number, and email address.

Listing information: Car details, photos, price, and description you post.

Usage data: App activity, search preferences, and interactions with other users.

Device information: Type of device, IP address, and operating system.

2. How We Use Your Information

We use your information to:

Provide and improve Drivo’s services.

Display your listings to other users.

Enable communication between buyers and sellers.

Prevent fraud and ensure user safety.

Comply with legal obligations.

3. How We Protect Your Data

We use appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. However, no online service is completely secure, and users share information at their own risk.

4. Sharing Information

We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may share limited data with:

Service providers that help us operate the platform.

Authorities if required by law or to prevent illegal activities.

5. Your Rights

You can request to view, edit, or delete your account and personal data by contacting us at info@drivo-cars.com
.

6. Children’s Privacy

Drivo is not intended for users under 18 years old.

7. Updates to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted in the app and take effect immediately upon publication.
